            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="h-px bg-gray-200 my-6"></div>

        <ul class="space-y-4 mt-8">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5 text-black flex-shrink-0 mr-3"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-base"
              ><strong>Free updates</strong> to any 1.x version</span
